 <p class="intro">We will be regularly hosting classes at our facility or can bring a class to you and your team. <a title="Contact DMA Floors to share what kind of class you're interested in." href="https://trimediaus.com/forDMA/contact-us.php">Contact us</a> if there is a class that you would like for us to bring to you.</p>
<p><a name="courses"></a>
<h2>Current Offerings</h2>
<p>If there is a particular subject that you are interested in, please let us know and we will look for a class that fulfills your needs.</p>
